name: Gradual Script Hoodie (Black)
description:
This is our new Gradual Script premium hoodie that has the letters "Gradual" vinyl cut onto the hoodie then has a custom woven label sewn onto the bottom of it (only certain ones shall have woven labels sewn into them due to seperation process). This is a high quality product.

Please allow 10 days before contacting us about your order as we use a supplier for the t-shirts and have to wait for them before we can receive them to sew on our labels.

name: Gradual Beanie (Black)
description:
This is a high quality product which has our custom digitized embroidery design embroidered onto Beechfield turn up beanies which are suitable for both summer and winter.

The beanie cannot be adjusted at the front but is able to be adjust at the back due to the process embroidering through the beanie to ensure it's 100% secure and will last.

The pictures provided aren't mock ups, they are actual pictures of the product.
